We have neither engaged in any operations nor generated any revenues to date. Our only activities through September 30, 2022 were organizational activities, those necessary to prepare for the Initial Public Offering, described below, and searching to identify a target business with which to consummate an initial Business Combination. We do not expect to generate any operating revenues until after the completion of our Business Combination. We generate non-operating income in the form of interest income on marketable securities held in the Trust Account. We incur expenses as a result of being a public company (for legal, financial reporting, accounting and auditing compliance), as well as for due diligence expenses.
For the year ended September 30, 2022, we had net income of $16,761,599, which consisted of change in fair value of warrants of $15,595,833, and interest earned on marketable securities held in Trust Account of $2,395,997, offset by operating and formation costs of $800,029 and provision for income taxes of $430,202.
